descriptionHTML:
Attention: only compatible on devices with ANDROID WEAR OPERATING SYSTEM.

Let's start spin forever with your own digital fidget spinner everywhere you go on your wrist.
Take the stress of the day by spinning this virtual toy, try to get the maximum speed and you will receive a surprise. Includes three spinners Neon, Metalic and Nuclear.
What you see is what you get.

V1.0 Watch face for round and square smartwatch, includes environment mode, animations and interactive mode.
